import React from 'react'
import { ListGroup, ListGroupItem } from 'reactstrap'
import {
    BrowserRouter as Router,
    Switch,
    Route,
    Link
  } from "react-router-dom";

function Menu() {
    return (
        <ListGroup>
            <Link tag="a" to="/" action >
                Home 
            </Link>
            <Link tag="a" to="/Addcourse" action >
                Add Course
            </Link>
            <Link tag="a" to="Allcourses" action >
                View Course
            </Link>
            <Link tag="a" to="#" action >
                ABout Us
            </Link>
            <Link tag="a" to="#" action >
                Contact 
            </Link>
        </ListGroup>
    )
}

export default Menu
